0Soren%20in%20Jharkhand%20or%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20in%20Bihar%2C%20false%20cases%20are%20being%20filed%20against%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rai%20said%20that%20Delhi%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20fortress%20to%20prevent%20protests%20by%20AAP%20leaders.%20%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal's%20family%20has%20been%20placed%20under%20house%20arrest.%20The%20AAP%20headquarters%20was%20sealed%20yesterday%20even%20as%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20in%20place%20and%20we%20are%20preparing%20for%20the%20elections.%20The%20Congress's%20accounts%20have%20been%20seized.%20Now%2C%20India's%20oldest%20party%20is%20not%20able%20to%20run%20a%20campaign%20for%20the%20polls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Congress%20chief%20Arvinder%20Singh%20Lovely%2C%20too%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20democracy%3F%20There's%20no%20level-playing%20field%20for%20us.%20You%20are%20arresting%20elected%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%20seizing%20accounts%20for%20India's%20oldest%20political%20party.%C2%A0%26quot%3BOur%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20waged%20a%20battle%20to%20save%20democracy.%20The%20Congress%20will%20not%20step%20back%20at%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPM%20leader%20Rajeev%20Kunwar%20said%20leaders%20of%20all%20INDIA%20allies%20will%20come%20together%20on%20March%2031.%20%26quot%3BWe%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%2C%20we%20will%20not%20tolerate%20attacks%20on%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rai%20said%20they%20will%20ask%20for%20permission%20from%20local%20authorities%20for%20the%20rally.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20alarming%20for%20democracy%20if%20we%20don't%20get%20permission.%26quot%3B%20The%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief%20said%20they%20are%20hopeful%20that%20the%20authorities%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20hold%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711269240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fv