sed%20following%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Sajid%2C%20a%20familiar%20face%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20who%20ran%20a%20barber%20shop%20opposite%20the%20victims'%20residence%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20double%20murder.%20Sajid%2C%20known%20to%20the%20children's%20father%2C%20Vinod%20Singh%2C%20visited%20their%20house%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20borrowing%20Rs%205%2C000.%20However%2C%20moments%20after%20being%20handed%20the%20money%2C%20Sajid%20launched%20a%20savage%20assault%20on%20the%20children%20as%20their%20mother%20prepared%20tea%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20gaining%20entry%20into%20the%20household%2C%20Sajid%20allegedly%20asked%20Aayush%20(11)%20to%20take%20him%20to%20his%20mother's%20beauty%20salon%20upstairs.%20Upon%20reaching%20the%20second%20floor%2C%20Sajid%20allegedly%20switched%20off%20the%20lights%20before%20launching%20a%20vicious%20assault%20on%20Aayush%20with%20a%20knife.%20As%20Sajid%20slashed%20Aayush's%20throat%2C%20his%20younger%20brother%20Ahaan%20(6)%20entered%20the%20room.%20Sajid%20then%20grabbed%20Ahaan%20and%20stabbed%20him%20multiple%20times%20as%20well.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20targeted%20their%20other%20sibling%2C%20Piyush%2C%20though%20the%20seven-year-old%20managed%20to%20escape%2C%20sustaining%20minor%20injuries%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20assault%2C%20Sajid%20fled%20the%20scene%20along%20with%20his%20brother%20Javed%2C%20who%20was%20reportedly%20waiting%20outside%20with%20a%20motorcycle.%20However%2C%20their%20escape%20was%20short-lived%20as%20Sajid%20was%20later%20confronted%20by%20the%20police%20and%20killed%20in%20an%20encounter.%20The%20encounter%20resulted%20in%20injuries%20to%20a%20police%20personnel%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaved%2C%20the%20co-accused%2C%20was%20on%20the%20run%20but%20has%20since%20surrendered%20to%20Bareilly%20police.%20In%20a%20video%20message%2C%20Javed%20claimed%20innocence%2C%20stating%20that%20he%20possesses%20call%20recordings%20suggesting%20his%20brother's%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%20murdered%20children%2C%20Vinod%20Singh%2C%20has%20called%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20circumstances%20surrounding%20the%20murders.%20He%20has%20urged%20the%20authorities%20to%20refrain%20from%20resorting%20to%20encounters%20and%20instead%20ensure%20Javed's%20arrest%20to%20uncover%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20heinous%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20know%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinod%20Singh%20said%2C%20seeking%20answers%20from%20the%20authorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJaved%20must%20be%20questioned%20so%20that%20we%20know%20why%20they%20did%20this.%20If%20he%20is%20killed%20in%20an%20encounter%2C%20the%20secret%20will%20never%20come%20out.%20Others%20may%20be%20involved%20too.%20We%20need%20to%20know%20if%20my%20children%20were%20killed%20as%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy.%20They%20would%20have%20killed%20others%20in%20the%20family%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20into%20the%20case%20is%20still%20ongoing%20with%20the%20police%20trying%20to%20establish%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20gruesome%20murders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711268340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ft6523es8_budaun-double-murder-_625x300_24_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdemanding-answers-father-of-budaun-murder-victims-sets-bike-on-fire-5301454%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20father%20of%20the%20two%20children%20brutally%20murdered%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Budaun%2C%20concerned%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20surrounding%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20double%20murder%2C%20set%20a%20bike%20on%20fire%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt