%20over-the-counter%20transactions%20related%20to%20government%20transactions%20up%20to%20the%20normal%20working%20hours%20on%20March%2030%20and%20March%2031%2C%202024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20annual%20closing%20of%20government%20accounts%2C%20RBI%20said%20that%20electronic%20transactions%20can%20be%20done%20till%20the%20stipulated%20time%20on%20both%20days%E2%80%94Saturday%20and%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTransactions%20through%20National%20Electronic%20Funds%20Transfer%20(NEFT)%20and%20Real%20Time%20Gross%20Settlement%20(RTGS)%20System%20will%20continue%20up%20to%202400%20hours%20as%20hitherto%20on%20March%2031%2C%202024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20facilitate%20government%20receipts%20and%20payments%2C%20the%20banks%20will%20conduct%20special%20clearing%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20government%20cheques%20both%20on%20March%2030%20and%2031%2C%202024%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20this%20necessary%20arrangement%2C%20RBI%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CSpecial%20clearing%20will%20be%20conducted%20for%20government%20cheques%20both%20on%20March%2030%20%26amp%3B%2031%2C%202024.%20Agency%20Banks%20are%20hereby%20advised%20that%20all%20cheques%20related%20to%20Government%20accounts%20may%20be%20presented%20on%20such%20clearing.%20The%20timing%20for%20the%20presentation%20and%20return%20clearing%20of%20instruments%20for%20these%20special%20clearing%20sessions%20for%20government%20cheques%20will%20be%20intimated%20in%20due%20course.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERBI%20also%20said%20that%20the%20reporting%20window%20of%20March%2031%20will%20remain%20open%20till%20noon%20on%20April%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20informing%20about%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20agency%20banks%20for%20the%20public%20on%20Sunday%E2%80%94March%2031%E2%80%94was%20previously%20released%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frbidocs.rbi.org.in%2Frdocs%2Fnotificati