r%20would%20be%20blamed%20if%20the%20big-hitting%20West%20Indian%20fails%20to%20shine%20in%20the%20coming%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20not%20go%20ahead%20of%20ourselves%2C%20he%20batted%20well%2C%20and%20it's%20got%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20anyone%20coming%20into%20there%20(KKR).%20If%20he%20doesn't%20do%20well%20in%20the%20next%20few%20innings%2C%20will%20you%20blame%20Gautam%20Gambhir%3F%20Let's%20take%20it%20a%20little%20bit%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Russell%20was%20undoubtedly%20brilliant%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20Gavaskar%20also%20highlighted%20how%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20bowlers%20failed%20to%20execute%20their%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20saw%20someone%20like%20Bhuveneshwar%20Kumar%2C%20who%20was%20practising%20his%20yorkers%20so%20well%20on%20the%20practise%20pitches%2C%20bowled%20leg-deliveries%20(in%20the%20match)%20which%20was%20everything%20in%20the%20arc%20for%20Andre%20Russell...%20When%20somebody%20like%20Russell%20is%20hitting%20the%20ball%20into%20the%20stands%2C%20nobody%20can%20stop%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20game%2C%20Russell%20gave%20a%20little%20emotional%20speech%2C%20highlighting%20his%20love%20for%20the%20Knight%20Riders%20and%20what%20wearing%20the%20franchise's%20jersey%20means%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20stuff%20pop%20on%20my%20Insta%20and%20I%20realise%20how%20well%20I%20am%20striking%20the%20ball.%20Shows%20that%20you%20are%20doing%20well.%20I%20have%20tried%20to%20react%20with%20whatever%20comes%20my%20way.%20Over%20the%20last%202%20years%2C%20bowlers%20have%20their%20plans%20against%20me.%20I%20have%20been%20digging%20out%20the%20runs%2C%20and%20I%20know%20everyone%20has%20a%20plan%20for%20me.%20(On%20his%20journey%20with%20KKR)%20I%20was%20on%20the%20bench%20early%20on%2C%20and%20just%20tried%20to%20make%20myself%20useful.%20This%20franchise%20means%20a%20lot%