rnment%20enabled%20women%20to%20travel%20in%20buses%20free%20of%20cost%20-%20AC%20buses%20included%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhis-pink-ticket-scheme-is-more-than-just-a-free-bus-ride-2126485%5C%22%3Ewith%20a%20'pink%20ticket'%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20wasn't%20just%20to%20make%20transportation%20convenient%2C%20but%20also%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20and%20progress%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fwont-be-tolerated-arvind-kejriwal-warns-action-against-drivers-who-dont-stop-buses-for-women-4045029%5C%22%3Ewomen%20across%20the%20city%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Addressing%20gender%20disparities%20in%20urban%20transit%20helps%20create%20a%20safe%20and%20economical%20commuting%20option%20for%20women%20while%20also%20symbolising%20a%20larger%20commitment%20to%20their%20empowerment%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20The%20step%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20transformative.%20Be%20it%20for%20education%2C%20employment%20or%20leisure%2C%20since%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20female%20ridership%20in%20buses%2C%20a%20jump%20from%2033%25%20to%20roughly%2044%25.%20Currently%2C%20approximately%2011%20lakh%20women%20travel%20for%20free%20in%20Delhi's%20buses%20every%20day.%20More%20than%20100%20crore%20pink%20tickets%20were%20sold%20as%20of%20February%202023%2C%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20spending%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20on%20the%20scheme.%20Moreover%2C%20safety%20measures%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmcd-schools-to-get-10-786-cctv-cameras-4633278%5C%22%3ECCTV%20surveillance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20panic%20buttons%2C%20and%20vehicle%20tracking%20systems%20are%20installed%20in%2096%25%20of%20operational%20buses%20to%20further%20strengthen%20the%20sense%20of%20security%20for%20women%20as%20they%20traverse%20the%20city.%20A%20greater%20presence%20of%20women%20in%20public%20spaces%20also%20builds%20safer%20spaces%20for%20other%20women%2C%20who%20feel%20encouraged%20to%20step%20out%20and%20pursue%20their%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Changing%20Economic%20Landscape%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20the%20free%20bus%20transportation%20scheme%20for%20women%20has%20also%20acted%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20enhancing%20their%20labour%20force%20participation%2C%20thereby%20helping%20the%20economic%20strain%20on%20low-income%20households%20and%20helping%20bridge%20the%20gender%20divide%20at%20the%20grassroots.%20This%20has%20also%20contributed%20to%20Delhi's%20economic%20landscape%2C%20which%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20surge%20in%20per%20capita%20income%20from%20%E2%82%B92.47%20lakh%20per%20annum%20in%202014%20to%20%E2%82%B94.62%20lakh%20per%20annum%20currently%2C%20nearly%20doubling%20and%20surpassing%20the%20national%20average%20by%202.5%20times.%20Contrary%20to%20misinformed%20claims%20that%20%26quot%3Bfree%20bus%20rides%20is%20bad%20economics%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20fiscal%20prudence%20has%20ensured%20a%20surplus%20budget%2C%20which%20underscores%20the%20financial%20stability%20of%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%20today%2C%20the%20winds%20of%20change%20continue%20to%20blow%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-the-eligibility-criteria-for-mukhyamantri-mahila-samman-yojana-announced-by-aap-5173327%5C%22%3EMukhyamantri%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Delhi%20budget%202024-2025.%20This%20scheme%20aims%20to%20help%20millions%20of%20women%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20come%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds.%20By%20offering%20financial%20assistance%20for%20personal%20and%20professional%20development%2C%20the%20programme%20aims%20to%20bolster%20women's%20socio-economic%20independence.%20It%20extends%20financial%20support%20to%20women%20who%20have%20historically%20faced%20barriers%2C%20thus%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20society%20where%20women%20can%20thrive%20independently.%20With%20this%20initiative%2C%20women%20are%20empowered%20to%20break%20free%20from%20the%20shackles%20of%20financial%20dependence%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20pursue%20their%20aspirations.%20It%20heralds%20a%20new%20dawn%20of%20progress%20for%20women%20in%20the%20city%2C%20bringing%20us%20closer%20to%20a%20reality%20where%20gender%20equality%20isn't%20just%20an%20aspiration%20but%20a%20lived%20experience%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Girl%20Student%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mukhyamantri%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20is%20just%20one%20facet%20of%20Delhi's%20approach%20to%20women's%20empowerment%2C%20which%20builds%20upon%20the%20foundation%20of%20past%20schemes%20aimed%20at%20fostering%20progress%20in%20various%20domains.%20For%20instance%2C%20under%20%C2%A0AAP%2C%20the%20capital's%20government%20schools%20are%20today%20providing%20world-class%20education%20to%20over%209%20lakh%20girls.%20Many%20of%20them%20often%20outperform%20their%20male%20counterparts.%20Initiatives%20such%20as%20free%20textbooks%2C%20uniforms%2C%20and%20specialised%20STEM%20education%20for%20them%20ensure%20that%20no%20girl%20is%20left%20behind%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20knowledge%20and%20opportunities.%20This%20year%2C%20933%20girls%20from%20Delhi%20government%20schools%20cleared%20the%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%2C%20while%20123%20made%20the%20cut%20in%20the%20JEE%20exam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20commitment%20to%20women's%20health%2C%20too%2C%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20establishment%20and%20expansion%20of%20accessible%20healthcare%20facilities%20like%20the%20women-centric%20Mahila%20Mohalla%20Clinics%2C%20which%20cater%20to%20women's%20needs%20specifically%2C%20alongside%20the%20regular%20Mohalla%20Clinics%20and%20Anganwadi%20Hubs.%20These%20initiatives%20have%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20improving%20medical%20outcomes%20for%20women%2C%20particularly%20those%20from%20marginalised%20sections%2C%20ensuring%20that%20every%20woman%20has%20access%20to%20quality%20healthcare%20services%20in%20her%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen's%20Safety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20aren't%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20elected%20government%2C%20with%202.60%20lakh%20CCTV%20cameras%20under%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20CCTV%20Scheme%20(that%20is%2C%201%2C820%20cameras%20per%20square%20mile)%2C%2087%2C000%20streetlights%20on%20roads%20and%202.80%20lakh%20LED%20street%20lights%20installed%20within%20colonies%20under%20the%20Mukhyamantri%20Delhi%20Street%20Lights%20Scheme%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20ensure%20adequate%20safety%20for%20women%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kejriwal%20government%20is%20also%20providing%20free%20electricity%20and%20water%2024x7%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20ease%20monthly%20expenditure%20concerns%20for%20women%20in%20many%20households.%20It%20has%20championed%20women's%20economic%20empowerment%20through%20initiatives%20that%20promote%20entrepreneurship%2C%20self-help%20groups%2C%20and%20access%20to%20microfinance%20loans.%20This%20comprehensive%20approach%20has%20not%20only%20uplifted%20individual%20women%20but%20is%20also%20contributing%20to%20a%20positive%20change%20within%20families%20and%20communities%2C%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20and%20fostering%20a%20culture%20of%20inclusivity%20and%20opportunity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeading%20By%20Example%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20gender%20mainstreaming%20and%20gender-responsive%20budgeting%20and%20planning%20serves%20as%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20governance%20in%20action.%20It%20can%20set%20an%20example%20for%20other%20governments%20too.%20By%20investing%20in%20women's%20health%2C%20education%2C%20safety%2C%20social%20mobility%20and%20economic%20empowerment%2C%20the%20city%20is%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20future%20where%20every%20woman%20can%20realise%20her%20full%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20other%20regions%20strive%20to%20emulate%20Delhi's%20successes%2C%20it%20has%20become%20increasingly%20evident%20that%20prioritising%20women's%20empowerment%20isn't%20just%20a%20moral%20imperative-it's%20essential%20for%20building%20a%20more%20equitable%20and%20prosperous%20future%20for%20all.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20an%20advocate%20and%20senior%20AAP%20leader)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711258800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Frft8pta_delhi-women-bus-ride-twitter_625x300_03_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fgovernance-in-action-on-aaps-approach-to-empowering-women-in-delhi-5300555%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20gender%20mainstreaming%20and%20gender-responsive%20budgeting%20and%20planning%20serves%20as%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20governance%20in%20action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fgovernance-in-action-on-aaps-approach-to-empowering-women-in-delhi-5300555%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AAP's%20Big%20Protest%20Today%20Amid%20Court%20Setback%20For%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDelhi%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20said%20all%20party%20MLAs%2C%20office-bearers%20will%20gather%20at%20Shaheedi%20Park%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20BJP%20-%20which%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20alleges%20is%20misusing%20central%20agencies%20to%2