20Minister%20added%20in%20his%20message.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20will%20take%20up%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20request%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20which%20he%20has%20challenged%20his%20arrest%20as%20well%20as%20a%20lower%20court's%20order%20granting%20the%20ED%20his%20custody%20for%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20chief%20was%20arrested%20on%20Thursday%20and%2C%20the%20next%20day%2C%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20in%20Delhi%20had%20remanded%20him%20in%20the%20Probe%20Agency's%20custody%20till%20March%2028.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20central%20agency%20has%20accused%20the%20AAP%20leader%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspirator%26quot%3B.%20The%20ED%20believes%20the%20now-scrapped%20policy%20provided%20an%20impossibly%20high%20profit%20margin%20of%20nearly%20185%20per%20cent%20for%20retailers%20and%2012%20per%20cent%20for%20wholesalers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711258740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjf7uum44_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_22_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrested-delhi-chief-minister-bjp-ed-delhi-liquor-policy-aaps-protest-against-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-today-india-bloc-to-join-5300074%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20has%20planned%20a%20protest%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20today%20against%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrested-delhi-chief-minister-bjp-ed-delhi-liquor-policy-aaps-protest-against-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-today-india-bloc-to-join-5300074%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20CM%20Kejriwal%20iss