%20country%20said%20it%20expected%20India%20to%20apply%20%26quot%3Bbasic%20democratic%20principles%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20a%20fair%20trial%20for%20the%20jailed%20leader.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20German%20foreign%20ministry%20was%20asked%20about%20Berlin's%20stand%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister's%20arrest%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Responding%20to%20the%20question%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20Germany%20had%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20case.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20note%2C%20India%20is%20a%20democratic%20country.%20We%20assume%20and%20expect%20that%20the%20standards%20relating%20to%20independence%20of%20Judiciary%20and%20basic%20democratic%20principles%20will%20also%20be%20applied%20in%20this%20case.%20Like%20anyone%20facing%20accusations%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20entitled%20to%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20trial%2C%20this%20includes%20he%20can%20make%20use%20of%20all%20available%20legal%20avenues%20without%20restrictions.%20The%20presumption%20of%20innocence%20is%20a%20central%20element%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20must%20apply%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20said%20the%20remarks%20%26quot%3Bundermined%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20judiciary%26quot%3B%20and%20were%20a%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20interference%20in%20India's%20internal%20matters%26quot%3B.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20summoned%20German%20envoy%20George%20Enzweiler%20to%20register%20an%20official%20protest.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20see%20such%20remarks%20as%20interfering%20in%20our%20judicial%20process%20and%20undermining%20the%20independence%20of%20our%20judiciary.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20a%20vibrant%20and%20robust%20democracy%20with%20rule%20of%20law.%20As%20in%20all%20legal%20cases%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20democratic%20world%2C%20law%20will%20take%20its%20own%20course%20in%20the%20instant%20matter.%20Biased%20assumptions%20made%20on%20this%20account%20are%20most%20unwarranted%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20after%20the%20meeting.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20chief%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20of%20being%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20conspirator%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20now-scrapped%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20which%20was%20implemented%20by%20his%20government%20to%20allegedly%20gain%20kickbacks%20from%20retailers%20and%20wholesalers.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20probe%20agency%20nine%20times%20before%20his%20arrest.%20He%20is%20currently%20in%20ED%20custody%20till%20March%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711250280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F17vl2e2c_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_22_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-india-slammed-germany-over-comments-on-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-5300230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20labelled%20Germany's%20comments%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20%26quot%3Bbiased%20and%20unwarranted%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20country%20said%20it%20expected%20India%20to%20apply%20%26quot%3Bbasic%20democratic%20principles%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20a%20fair%20trial%20for%20the%20jailed%20lead%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-india-slammed-germany-over-comments-on-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-5300230%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mexican%20forces%20search%20for%2024%20possible%20kidnapping%20victims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711248943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108742989%2Cimgsize-963943.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmexican-forces-search-for-24-possible-