rcing%20within%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wrote%20that%20the%20company%20is%20a%20smartphone%20manufacturer%20for%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20who%20want%20more%20of%20a%20digital%20appliance%20than%20a%20platform%20for%20tinkering%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20been%20its%20differentiating%20factor%20from%20businesses%20like%20Microsoft%20since%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20the%20DOJ's%20claims%20that%20Apple%20engages%20in%20anticompetitive%20behavior%20by%20making%20features%20on%20Apple%20phones%20work%20best%20when%20interacting%20with%20other%20products%20in%20the%20Apple%20ecosystem%20shouldn't%20require%20the%20government's%20intervention%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebecause%20even%20%26quot%3BGmail%20only%20works%20fully%20and%20properly%20in%20a%20special%20Gmail%20app.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMossberg%20noted%20that%2C%20in%20the%20suit%2C%20the%20DOJ%20had%20to%20narrowly%20define%20the%20market%20in%20which%20it%20alleges%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-apple-is-a-monopoly-antitrust-lawsuit-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20holds%20a%20monopoly%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3B'performance'%20phones%2C%20meaning%20expensive%20phones%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20%E2%80%94%20to%20back%20up%20its%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20claims%20the%20iPhone%20has%2070%25%20of%20that%20market%20in%20the%20US.%20That's%20like%20calling%20the%20best-selling%20expensive%20wine%20a%20monopoly%20when%20it%20actually%20has%20a%20modest%20overall%20market%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20Mossberg%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20DOJ%20acts%20as%20if%20there's%20a%20right%20for%20competitors%20to%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fantitrust-doj-lawsuit-apple-green-messages-android-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiMessage%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20proprietary%20to%20Apple.%20But%20since%20when%20must%20companies%20do%20such%20a%20thing%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3