2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChina%20stands%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20Nepal%20to%20take%20this%20visit%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20further%20deliver%20on%20the%20important%20common%20understandings%20between%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20deepen%20political%20mutual%20trust%2C%20pursue%20high-quality%20Belt%20and%20Road%20cooperation%2C%20expand%20exchanges%20and%20cooperation%20in%20various%20areas%20and%20strive%20for%20new%20progress%20in%20building%20China-Nepal%20strategic%20partnership%20of%20cooperation%20featuring%20ever-lasting%20friendship%20for%20development%20and%20prosperity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20China%20and%20Nepal%20were%20%E2%80%9Ctraditional%20friends%20and%20neighbours%20linked%20by%20mountains%20and%20rivers.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20our%20two%20countries%20maintained%20close%20high-level%20exchanges%20with%20deepening%20practical%20cooperation%20in%20various%20fields%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20two%20sides%20maintained%20close%20coordination%20and%20collaboration%20in%20regional%20and%20international%20affairs.%20Last%20September%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Prachanda%20paid%20an%20official%20visit%20to%20China%20and%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20reached%20important%20common%20understandings%20on%20growing%20the%20China-Nepal%20relations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lin%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20Shrestha%E2%80%99s%20visit%20also%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20China%20is%20suggesting%20Nepal%20to%20sign%20an%20implementation%20plan%20of%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Nepal%20is%20unlikely%20to%20sign%20the%20agreement%20ahead%20of%20a%20planned%20investment%20summit%20for%20which%20it%20is%20seeking%20the%20support%20of%20the%20international%20community%2C%20including%20India%2C%20the%20US%20and%20other%20democratic%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20was%20the%20first%20country%20to%20react%20on%20th