0defectors%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20(BRS)%2C%20while%20the%20fourth%20is%20a%20rank%20outsider%20to%20politics%20who%20will%20make%20his%20debut%20in%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20even%20more%20surprising%20is%20that%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20Khairatabad%20MLA%2C%20Danam%20Nagender%2C%20who%20won%20the%20assembly%20polls%20only%20three%20months%20ago%2C%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Congress%20even%20before%20he%20resigned%20from%20his%20former%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20four%20days%20after%20he%20posed%20for%20a%20photograph%20with%20chief%20minister%20and%20Telangana%20Congress%20committee%20president%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20while%20accepting%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20colours%2C%20he%20was%20declared%20its%20candidate%20from%20Secunderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20now%20petitioned%20assembly%20speaker%20G.%20Prasad%20Kumar%20seeking%20Nagender%E2%80%99s%20disqualification%20as%20per%20the%20anti-defection%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20BRS%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20G.%20Ranjith%20Reddy%2C%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Chevella%20and%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20poultry%20industry%3B%20and%20G.%20Sunitha%20Mahender%20Reddy%2C%20who%20is%20the%20zilla%20parishad%20chairperson%20of%20Vikarabad%20district%20%E2%80%93%20also%20got%20tickets%20as%20Congress%20candidates%20from%20Chevella%20and%20Malkajgiri%20constituencies%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjith%20Reddy%20and%20Nagender%20joined%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunitha%20Mahender%20Reddy%2C%20wife%20of%20BRS%20MLC%20and%20former%20minister%20Mahender%20Reddy%2C%20was%20earlier%20sounded%20out%20for%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20from%20Chevella%20but%20was%20accommodated%20at%20Malkajgiri%2C%20reportedly%20against%20her%20wishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Nagender%2C%20Mahender%20Reddy%20has%20also%20not%20resigned%20from%20the%20legislative%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Nagar