0the%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20were%20often%20confronted%20with%20questions%20on%20differential%20treatment%20for%20Kavitha%20by%20not%20arresting%20her%2C%20while%20the%20other%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20including%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20languished%20in%20jail%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20expressed%20relief%20that%20the%20question%20did%20not%20haunt%20them%20anymore%20and%20that%20they%20could%20freely%20approach%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20K.%20Nageshwar%20said%20the%20Congress%20is%20depending%20on%20defectors%20in%20its%20allotment%20of%20tickets%20wherever%20the%20party%20is%20not%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20it%20looked%20for%20outsiders%20in%20constituencies%20like%20Secunderabad%20and%20Malkajgiri%20within%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%E2%80%99s%20limits%2C%20where%20the%20party%20fared%20badly%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20It%20did%20not%20have%20a%20uniform%20policy%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20adopted%20a%20different%20strategy%20of%20identifying%20strong%20candidates%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20winnability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20state%20general%20secretary%20G.%20Premender%20Reddy%20said%20the%20party%20had%20plenty%20of%20candidates%20to%20choose%20from%20but%20looked%20for%20outsiders%20with%20winning%20chances%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20various%20equations%20and%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Congress%20committee%20working%20president%20B.%20Mahesh%20Kumar%20Goud%20recalled%20that%20one%20of%20the%20three%20BRS%20leaders%20who%20were%20given%20tickets%2C%20Nagender%2C%20was%20a%20former%20Congressman%20who%20jumped%20to%20the%20BRS%20after%20Telangana%20was%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20won%20as%20a%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20candidate%20from%20the%20Asifnagar%20assembly%20constituency%20in