.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fservices%2Faop-cambridge-core%2Fcontent%2Fview%2F944A18883970B826970525435AA4A837%2Fstamped-9781009171915c9_p183-206_CBO.pdf%2Fintersectional_water_justice_in_india_at_the_confluence_of_gender_caste_and_climate_change.pdf%5C%22%3Ewater%20scarcity%20%3C%2Fa%3Edue%20to%20the%20proliferation%20of%20tubewells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroundwater%20access%20becomes%20the%20preserve%20of%20the%20upper%20castes%20through%20the%20building%20of%20tubewells%20on%20private%20land%2C%20a%20form%20of%20access%20based%20on%20casteist%20social%20structures%20that%20limit%20land%20ownership%20among%20the%20lower%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20socio-economic%20status%20determines%20access%20to%20water%20and%20who%20uses%20more%20of%20the%20groundwater%20commons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETubewells%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20drying%20out%20of%20shallow%20wells%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F10455752.2015.1066835%3FjournalCode%3Drcns20%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThis%2520was%2520done%2520to%2520generate%2Cknowledge%2520about%2520the%2520watershed%2520project.%26text%3DCaste%2520is%2520a%2520pan-Indian%2520phenomenon.%5C%22%3Ewater%20lords%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20who%20dominate%20consumption%20of%20water.%20This%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20forces%20poor%20farmers%20to%20rely%20further%20on%20them%20for%20water%20supply%20in%20an%20already%20exploitative%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20caste%2C%20gender%20also%20becomes%20a%20determinant%20of%20communities%E2%80%99%20relationships%20with%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20are%20the%20face%20of%20water%20poverty%20in%20India.%20The%20responsibility%20of%20meeting%20families%E2%80%99%20water%20needs%20in%20rural%20India%20falls%20squarely%20on%20them%2C%20exacerbated%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fby-2080-india-could-lose-groundwater-by-3-times-the-current-rate-study%2Farticle67263183.ece%5C%22%