20was%20not%20at%20the%20helm%20and%20the%20process%20culminated%20earlier%20this%20month%20with%20the%20removal%20of%20234%20poplar%20and%20willow%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20trees%20were%20decaying%20and%20posed%20a%20threat%20to%20life%20and%20property%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prof%20Bashir%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20more%20than%204000%20college%20students%20and%20staff%2C%20they%20had%20to%20be%20removed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20forest%20department%20official%20confirmed%20that%20the%20college%20had%20referred%20the%20trees%20for%20evaluation%20to%20the%20Social%20Forestry%20Department%20after%20which%20they%20were%20put%20up%20for%20auction.%20However%2C%20the%20official%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20the%20evaluation%20report%20of%20the%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20listed%20heritage%20college%20and%20a%20Grade-1%20heritage%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinagar-based%20art%20conservator%20and%20historian%20Saleem%20Beg%20mentioned%2C%20adding%20that%20that%20the%20plantation%2C%20which%20was%20an%20attraction%20among%20filmmakers%20and%20tourists%20in%20the%20city%2C%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20original%20layout%20that%20synchronised%20the%20entries%2C%20pathways%20and%20buildings%20of%20the%20college%20which%20was%20built%20in%201913.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22160932%2FScreenshot-2024-03-22-at-3.59.45.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22160932%2FScreenshot-2024-03-22-at-3.59.45.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22160932%2FScreenshot-2024-03-22-at-3.59.45-300x202.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22160932%2FScreenshot-2024-03-22-at-3.59.45-1024x689.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702848%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22808%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDozens%20of%20poplar%20trees%20were%20removed%20from%20a%20scenic%20avenue%20in%20Amar%20Singh%20College%2C%20which%20is%20a%20listed%20heritage%20college%20and%20a%20Grade-1%20heritage%20structure.%20Photo%3A%20Ubaid%20Mukhtar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20very%20inappropriate%20decision.%20The%20avenue%20has%20been%20the%20essential%20part%20of%20the%20built%20fabric%20that%20linked%20the%20main%20building%20with%20its%20natural%20settings.%20The%20college%20management%20should%20have%20retained%20the%20natural%20setting%20by%20protecting%20these%20trees.%20They%20should%20have%20known%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20Beg%2C%20who%20is%20the%20convener%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chapter%20of%20Indian%20National%20Trust%20for%20Art%20and%20Cultural%20Heritage%20(INTACH)%2C%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INTACH%20notified%20Amar%20Singh%20College%20as%20a%20Grade%201%20heritage%20structure%20in%202004.%20The%20college%20also%20figures%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Higher%20Education%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20heritage%20colleges%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%C2%A0However%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20not%20notified%20the%20college%20as%20a%20heritage%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INTACH%20carried%20out%20conservation%20works%20at%20the%20college%20which%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20government.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20college-related%20work%20was%20one%20of%20seven%20projects%20that%20won%20the%20prestigious%20Award%20of%20Merit%20in%20the%20UNESCO%20Asia-Pacific%20Awards%20for%20Cultural%20Heritage%20Conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22185823%2Fimage-1997.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22880%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22185823%2Fimage-1997.png%20737w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22185823%2Fimage-1997-300x300.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22185823%2Fimage-1997-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702881%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22880%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPoplar%20trees%20at%20the%20entrance%20to%20Amar%20Singh%20College%20in%20Srinagar.%20Photo%3A%20X%40Gaamuk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudents%20unhappy%20with%20the%20move%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20students%20who%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20college%20after%20the%20culmination%20of%20winter%20vacation%20earlier%20this%20month%20were%20shocked%20and%20visibly%20upset%20by%20the%20scenes%20of%20lopped%20logs%20of%20poplar%20trees%20scattered%20along%20the%20avenue%20which%20they%20had%20once%20beautified%20with%20their%20towering%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20been%20done%20is%20not%20right.%20The%20trees%20didn%E2%80%99t%20kill%20anyone.%20I%20used%20to%20see%20them%20on%20reels%20and%20photos%20of%20the%20college%20before%20I%20joined%20here%20last%20year.%20Now%20they%20are%20nowhere.%20It%20seems%20as%20if%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20college%20has%20been%20erased%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20first-year-student%2C%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Junaid%20Ahmad%2C%20an%20alumni%2C%20fondly%20recalled%20that%20the%20avenue%20presented%20the%20looks%20of%20a%20green%20tunnel%20which%20showed%20an%20impressive%20view%20of%20the%20main%20heritage%20building.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20avenue%20was%20an%20imposing%20feature%20of%20the%20college%20which%20conveyed%20to%20the%20students%20that%20they%20are%20in%20a%20very%20great%20and%20grand%20space.%20Sadly%20it%20has%20been%20flattened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%20and%20environmentalists%20express%20concern%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchitect%20Saima%20Iqbal%2C%20who%20led%20the%20INTACH%20conservation%20effort%2C%20said%20that%20the%20poplar%20avenues%20were%20important%20landscape%20elements%20for%20enhancing%20entrance%20experience%20of%20buildings%20and%20for%20providing%20vistas%2C%20shade%20and%20formality%20to%20the%20urban%20roads%20in%20the%20early%2020th%20century%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20historic%20avenue.%20It%20has%20a%20permanence%20and%20relevance%20of%20its%20own%2C%20an%20importance%20of%20its%20own%20and%20also%20a%20significance%20of%20its%20own.%20It%20had%20a%20specific%20purpose%20to%20give%20visitors%20a%20guided%20vista%20of%20the%20college.%20What%20has%20been%20done%20is%20a%20catastrophe%2C%E2%80%9D%20Iqbal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Srinagar-based%20environmentalist%2C%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20college%20has%20%E2%80%9Ceffectively%20wiped%20off%20a%20mini%20carbon%20sink%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20campus.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20avenues%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20preservation%20of%20micro-climatic%20conditions%20and%20also%20filter%20the%20air.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlaming%20the%20college%20management%20for%20the%20move%2C%20Beg%20asserted%20that%20the%20rules%20governing%20the%20conservation%20of%20notified%20heritage%20sites%20should%20have%20been%20factored%20in%20by%20them%20before%20culling%20the%20trees%20which%20are%20%E2%80%9Cequally%20important%E2%80%9D%20from%20a%20heritage%20point%20of%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20official%20guidelines%2C%20any%20proposal%20of%20drastic%20changes%20in%20notified%20heritage%20buildings%20or%20heritage%20landscapes%20has%20to%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20Heritage%20Conservation%20Committee%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20a%20secretary-level%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guidelines%20mention%20that%20Grade-1%20heritage%20buildings%20%E2%80%9Cdeserve%20careful%20preservation%E2%80%9D%20with%20%E2%80%9Cno%20intervention%E2%80%9D%20allowed%20inside%20the%20heritage%20building%20or%20in%20its%20natural%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20the%20college%20is%20not%20a%20notified%20structure%20but%20by%20extension%20the%20model%20bye%20laws%20should%20ipso%20facto%20apply%20to%20listed%20buildings%20and%20the%20state%20government-declared%20heritage%20colleges.%20Although%20the%20government%20declaration%20was%20meant%20for%20seeking%20funding%20for%20their%20preservation%2C%20but%20that%20definition%20is%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Beg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArt%20historian%20Hakim%20Sameer%20Hamdani%2C%20who%20has%20led%20major%20heritage%20conservation%20and%20restoration%20efforts%20in%20Srinagar%20underlined%20that%20people%20in%20Kashmir%20are%20not%20generally%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20heritage%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20a%20question%20of%20how%20do%20you%20value%20and%20what%20do%20you%20value%E2%80%9D%20as%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20understanding%20of%20natural%20heritage%20is%20largely%20limited%20to%20the%20protection%20of%20Chinar%20trees%20and%20Dal%20Lake.%C2%A0%20As%20a%20society%2C%20we%20have%20to%20re-understand%20what%20development%20means%2C%20what%20beautification%20means%20and%20what%20respect%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20past%20means%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hamdani%2C%20a%20Srinagar%20resident%20and%20author%20of%20the%20upcoming%20book%20on%20Srinagar%2C%20%E2%80%98City%20of%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Popular%20History%E2%80%99%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20college%20principal%2C%20a%20batch%20of%20conifers%20planted%20by%20the%20Social%20Forestry%20Department%20along%20the%20avenue%20some%20two%20years%20back%20wi