he%20new%20rankings%20system%20could%20be%20released%20soon%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Democracy%20Index%20being%20prepared%20by%20ORF%20went%20through%20a%20peer%20review%20process%20and%20expert%20analysis%20on%20the%20methodology%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20released%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20second%20source%20familiar%20with%20the%20development%20told%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20internal%20public%20policy%20think%20tank%20responsible%20for%20carrying%20out%20discussions%20within%20the%20Modi%20government%20regarding%20global%20rankings%2C%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20directly%20involved%20in%20creating%20the%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20per%3Cem%3E%20Al%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20they%20neither%20confirmed%20nor%20denied%20their%20involvement%20in%20assisting%20an%20external%20think%20tank%20in%20its%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20NITI%20Aayog%20told%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CNITI%20is%20not%20in%20the%20process%20of%20developing%20any%20Democracy%20Index.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20of%20India%20monitors%20select%20global%20indices%20%5Bby%20various%20global%20entities%5D%20to%20drive%20reforms%20and%20growth%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYet%20emails%20and%20the%20minutes%20of%20meetings%20held%20between%20government%20agencies%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20accessed%20and%20reviewed%20by%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20point%20to%20a%20growing%20urgency%20within%20the%20Modi%20administration%20on%20challenging%20setbacks%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20credentials%2C%20including%20through%20a%20report%20prepared%20by%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeclining%20press%20freedom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20exercise%20started%20in%202021%20after%20Freedom%20House%2C%20a%20US-based%20government-funded%20NGO%2C%20downgraded%20India%E2%80%99s%20status%20from%20%E2%80%98Free%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Fcountry%2Findia%2Ffreedom-world%2F2021%5C%22%3EPartly%20Free%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20attributed%20the%20downgrade%20to%20%E2%80%9Ca%20crackdown%20on%20expressions%20of%20dissent%20by%20the%20media%2C%20academics%2C%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20and%20protesters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20V-Dem%20Institute%2C%20based%20in%20Sweden%2C%20also%20classified%20India%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Celectoral%20autocracy%E2%80%9D%20in%202021.%20In%20its%202023%20report%2C%20it%20downgraded%20India%20further%2C%20classifying%20the%20country%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-autocratiser-v-dem-report-2023%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20worst%20autocratisers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economist%20Intelligence%20Unit%20ranked%20India%2053rd%20in%20its%202020%20Democracy%20Index%2C%20labelling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cflawed%20democracy%E2%80%9D%2C%20citing%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20and%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20special%20status%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20top%20officials%20from%20the%20central%20government%20ministries%20and%20departments%20such%20as%20home%20affairs%2C%20external%20affairs%20and%20the%20legislative%20departments%2C%20among%20others%2C%20were%20instructed%20by%20Cabinet%20Secretary%20Rajiv%20Gauba%20to%20monitor%20India%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20democracy%20indices%20and%20identify%20areas%20where%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20standing%20had%20declined%2C%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20began%20monitoring%20its%20performance%20in%2030%20global%20indices%2C%20with%20different%20ministries%20tasked%20with%20tracking%20individual%20ratings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20legislative%20department%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Law%20and%20Justice%20was%20assigned%20the%20EIU%E2%80%99s%20Democracy%20Index%20to%20watch.%20The%20NITI%20Aayog%20was%20asked%20to%20create%20a%20dashboard%20for%20monitoring%20data%20across%20all%20the%20indices%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20law%20ministry%20turned%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20High%20Commission%20in%20London%20to%20seek%20details%20from%20the%20EIU%20on%20its%20assessment%20of%20India.%20However%2C%20EIU%20refused%20to%20give%20details%20to%20the%20government%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Feiu-not-sharing-info-on-democracy-index-govt-101629050360548.html%5C%22%3Ereported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimon%20Baptist%2C%20chief%20economist%20at%20EIU%2C%20even%20tweeted%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20obvious%20reasons%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20check%20our%20scores%20with%20governments%20before%20release!%20We%20come%20up%20with%20our%20own%20independent%20assessment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20methodology%20and%20scores%20for%20all%20countries%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheEIU%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40theeiu%3C%2Fa%3E%20democracy%20index%20are%20available%20to%20anyone%20in%20this%2075%20page%20report%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20exact%20questions%20that%20we%20use%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20rankings%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlZdAMu71iL%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlZdAMu71iL%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNJ7yE7XOxy%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNJ7yE7XOxy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Simon%20Baptist%20EIU%20(%40baptist_simon)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbaptist_simon%2Fstatus%2F1427121609823772673%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20clearly%20indicates%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20concern%20about%20its%20declining%20democracy%20rankings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-ram-temple-india-democracy-pluralism-ram-guha-karan-thapar%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20Tamasha%20Around%20Ram%20Temple%20Should%20Worry%20Indians%20Who%20Believe%20in%20Democracy%2C%20Pluralism%3A%20Ram%20Guha%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControlling%20the%20data%20narrative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20the%20first%20instance%20when%20the%20government%20has%20tried%20to%20control%20the%20data%20narrative.%20Meanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Feconomy-policy%2Fmodi-s-suspect-gdp-numbers-have-done-real-damage-119061400400_1.html%5C%22%3Emisleading%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-hollowness-of-modi-governments-tall-claims-and-self-praise-on-economy%5C%22%3Eclaims%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20based%20on%20data%20is%20a%20separate%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20data%20journalist%20Pramit%20Bhattacharya%2C%20in%20his%20paper%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieendowment.org%2F2023%2F06%2F28%2Findia-s-statistical-system-past-present-future-pub-90065%5C%22%3Etitled%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20statistical%20system%3A%20past%2C%20present%20and%20future%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehighlighted%20well-known%20problems%20with%20Indian%20statistics.%20These%20include%20a%20%E2%80%9Cperceived%20lack%20of%20independence%20of%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Organisation%2C%20instances%20of%20government%20wanting%20to%20control%20the%20data%20narrative%2C%20conflict%20between%20the%20MOSPI%20(Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Programme%20Implementation)%20and%20various%20arms%20of%20government%20hurting%20quality%20and%20importance%20of%20statisticians%20at%20the%20central%20and%20state%20level%2C%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20financial%20and%20human%20resources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERathin%20Roy%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20UK-based%20Overseas%20Development%20Institute%2C%20told%20CNBC-TV18%E2%80%99s%20%3Cspan%3ELatha%20Venkatesh%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ethat%20despite%20bureaucratic%20squabbles%20that%20took%20place%20between%201950s%20and%201980s%2C%20the%20government%20had%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20statistical%20system%20because%20it%20needed%20that%20information%20to%20be%20able%20to%20plan%20forward.%20Now%20the%20government%20does%20not%20need%20it%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20major%20reason%20for%20the%20system%20being%20in%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-hollowness-of-modi-governments-tall-claims-and-self-praise-on-economy%5C%22%3EThe%20Hollowness%20of%20the%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Tall%20Claims%20and%20Self-Praise%20on%20Economy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBad%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20refocusses%20attention%20on%20another%20issue%3A%20bad%20data%2C%20or%20a%20misleading%20analysis%20of%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20for%20instance%2C%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mospi.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpublication_reports%2FAR_PLFS_2022_23N.pdf%3Fdownload%3D1%5C%22%3EPeriodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS)%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20July%202022%20to%20June%202023%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eemphasised%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20unemployment%20rate%20for%20individuals%20aged%2015%20and%20above%20reached%20a%20six-year%20low.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20detailed%20look%20at%20the%20numbers%20showed%20that%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20individuals%20in%20India%20are%20engaging%20in%20self-employment%20or%20unpaid%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20only%20jobs%20that%20are%20getting%20created%20are%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cself-employment%E2%80%9D%20type.%20When%20an%20economy%20grows%2C%20businesses%20employ%20people.%20When%20an%20economy%20struggles%2C%20people%20lose%20their%20regular%20jobs%2C%20and%20become%20%E2%80%9Cself-employed%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-economics%2Findia-latest-employment-data-plfs-8984873%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20analysing%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevelopment%20economist%20Santosh%20Mehrotra%2C%20along%20with%20other%20economists%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Feconomists-say-niti-aayog-claims-on-poverty-reduction-distort-the-truth%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20claim%20on%20poverty%20reduction%20distorts%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20poverty%20have%20fallen%20when%20job%20growth%20and%20real%20wages%20have%20come%20down%3F%20Nearly%20190%20million%20workers%20(2021-22)%20in%20India%20are%20earning%20just%20up%20to%20Rs%20100%20per%20day%20(in%20real%20terms%20at%202010%20prices)%20which%20can%20be%20categorised%20as%20absolutely%20poor%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20just%20106.1%20million%20workers%20in%202011-12.%20Similarly%2C%20nearly%20144%20million%20workers%20are%20earning%20between%20Rs%20100%20and%20Rs%20200%20in%202021-22.%20This%20indicates%20the%20need%20for%20interrogating%20labour%20market%20conditions%20in%20India%2C%20before%20jumping%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20India%20has%20been%20able%20to%20end%20poverty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Feconomists-divided-over-poverty-decline-claims-by-sbi-niti-aayog-124022801156_1.html%5C%22%3Et