ts%20to%20clear%20the%20exam.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20FMP%20has%20given%20UPSC%20aspirants%20a%20choice%2C%20which%20is%20what%20stands%20out%20the%20most%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Free%20UPSC%20CSE%20Coaching%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095.jpg%201066w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345402%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22710%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEx-IRS%20officer%20and%20educator%20Ravi%20Kapoor%20(on%20the%20left)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecognising%20the%20gap%20in%20the%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20an%20entire%20cottage%20industry%20has%20been%20built%20on%20UPSC%20coaching.%20Walk%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22h