re%20any%20legal%20advice%20that%20she%20would%20give%20to%20everyone%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20laws%20that%20concern%20you.%20Legal%20knowledge%20is%20just%20as%20important%20as%20financial%20education.%20As%20consumers%2C%20being%20aware%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344779%2Fworld-consumers-rights-day-landmark-judgements-consumer-law-in-india-online-orders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance.%20Read%20up%20on%20things%20related%20to%20you%20and%20your%20line%20of%20work.%20Know%20your%20rights%20as%20a%20tenant%20or%20property%20owner%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Pictures%20Courtesy%20Shreya%20Sharma)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710766089000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shreya%20Sharma%20started%20'Rest%20The%20Case'%20in%202021%2C%20a%20legal%20aggregator%20platform%20that%20provides%20a%20list%20of%201%2C200%20specialised%20lawyers%20across%20200%20cities%20in%20India.%20It%20also%20provides%20basic%20legal%20templates%20like%20rent%20agreements%20and%20explains%20legal%20terms%20that%20everyone%20should%20know.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345065%2Fhow-to-find-a-lawyer-legal-startup-pune-shreya-sharma-divorce-family-court-business-property-law-rent-agreement%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20Raspberries%2C%20Blueberries%20in%20India%3F%20Woman%20Uses%20Low-Cost%20Innovation%20to%20Run%20Berry%20Biz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20yea